    <main class="main-panel">
      <div class="page-header-area">
        <h1 class="page-title">Data Table</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">A structured table for tabular, row-based data with toolbar, selectable rows, column headers, a footer with pagination, and a floating bulk-action bar that appears when rows are selected.</p>
        <nav class="content-tabs">
          <button class="tab-item active">Overview</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Style</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Usage</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Code</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Accessibility</button>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="main-content-area">
        <div class="main-content-inner">

        <!-- ========== OVERVIEW ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-overview">
          <h3 id="anatomy" class="doc-h3">Anatomy</h3>
          <div class="anatomy-diagram" style="padding-top:56px;padding-bottom:56px;">
            <div class="dt-wrapper" style="margin:12px auto;max-width:680px;position:relative;overflow:visible;">
              <!-- 1 Toolbar: marker left of wrapper, horizontal line pointing right -->
              <div style="position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 6px);top:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
              <div class="dt-toolbar" style="overflow:visible;position:relative;">
                <!-- 2 Search: marker above the search input -->
                <div style="position:absolute;left:130px;top:-28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div style="width:2px;height:10px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                <div class="dt-search" style="width:260px;">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
                  <input type="text" placeholder="Search...">
                </div>
                <div style="flex:1;"></div>
                <div style="position:relative;">
                  <!-- 3 Filter: marker above Filter button -->
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);top:-38px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">3</span><div style="width:2px;height:10px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                  <button class="dt-toolbar-btn with-label"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 4h18l-7 8v6l-4 2v-8z"/></svg> Filter</button>
                </div>
                <div style="position:relative;">
                  <!-- 4 Overflow: marker above overflow button -->
                  <div style="position:absolute;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);top:-38px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">4</span><div style="width:2px;height:10px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                  <button class="dt-toolbar-btn"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1"/></svg></button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="position:relative;">
                <!-- 5 Select-all: marker left of header row, horizontal line pointing right -->
                <div style="position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 6px);top:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">5</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                <!-- 6 Column headers: marker right of Name column, horizontal line pointing left -->
                <div style="position:absolute;left:260px;top:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><div style="width:20px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div><span class="anat-marker-inline">6</span></div>
                <table class="dt-table">
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></th>
                      <th>Name</th>
                      <th>Type</th>
                      <th>Status</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>MacBook Pro</td><td>Laptop</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr>
                    <tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>iPhone 15</td><td>Mobile</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
                <!-- 7 Rows: marker left of first data row, horizontal line pointing right -->
                <div style="position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 6px);top:70px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">7</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="dt-footer" style="position:relative;overflow:visible;">
                <!-- 8 Footer: marker left of footer -->
                <div style="position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">8</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                <!-- 9 Pagination: marker right of wrapper, horizontal line pointing left -->
                <div style="position:absolute;left:calc(100% + 6px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:row-reverse;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:20;"><span class="anat-marker-inline">9</span><div style="width:28px;height:2px;background:#2563eb;"></div></div>
                <div class="dt-footer-left">Rows per page <select class="dt-rows-select"><option>20</option></select> <span>1&ndash;20 of 243</span></div>
                <div class="dt-pagination">
                  <button class="dt-page-btn">&lsaquo; Previous</button>
                  <button class="dt-page-btn">Next &rsaquo;</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="anat-legend" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);">
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div><strong>Toolbar</strong><span>Top action strip. Contains refresh, search, filter, and overflow controls. Toggleable via Toolbar=true/false.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div><strong>Search</strong><span>Free-text search input. Filters rows across all visible columns or a user-defined subset.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">3</span><div><strong>Filter</strong><span>Dropdown with column-level filter chips. Applied filters persist across pagination.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">4</span><div><strong>Overflow (&#8942;)</strong><span>Low-frequency actions: column chooser, density, export-all, refresh.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">5</span><div><strong>Select-all Checkbox</strong><span>Toggles selection on all visible rows. Shows indeterminate state when selection is partial.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">6</span><div><strong>Column Headers</strong><span>Semibold 13px labels using BG-Secondary-alt. Support sort / filter affordances per column.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">7</span><div><strong>Rows</strong><span>Repeating data rows with a leading checkbox + N cells. Default 40px, hover + selected states.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">8</span><div><strong>Footer</strong><span>Rows-per-page selector, range (1&ndash;20 of 243), and pagination. Toggleable via Footer=true/false.</span></div></div>
            <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">9</span><div><strong>Pagination / Bulk Bar</strong><span>Previous / Next controls. Replaced by the floating bulk-action bar when rows are selected.</span></div></div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div style="margin-bottom:64px;">
            <h2 id="live-demo" class="doc-section-title" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Preview</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:28px;">Interact with a Data Table &mdash; tick rows to reveal the bulk-action bar, toggle the header checkbox to select all.</p>
            <div class="demo-container">
<div class="demo-canvas" style="padding:32px;">
                <div class="dt-wrapper" id="live-dt">
                  <div class="dt-toolbar">
                    <div class="dt-search">
                      <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
                      <input type="text" placeholder="Search devices...">
                    </div>
                    <div style="flex:1;"></div>
                    <button class="dt-toolbar-btn" title="Refresh"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h5M20 20v-5h-5M4 9a8 8 0 0114-4M20 15a8 8 0 01-14 4"/></svg></button>
                    <button class="dt-toolbar-btn with-label"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 4h18l-7 8v6l-4 2v-8z"/></svg> Filter</button>
                    <button class="dt-toolbar-btn" title="More"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1"/></svg></button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="dt-table-scroll">
                    <table class="dt-table">
                      <thead>
                        <tr>
                          <th class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox" id="dt-head-check"></th>
                          <th>Name</th>
                          <th>Type</th>
                          <th>Status</th>
                          <th>Last Seen</th>
                          <th>Owner</th>
                        </tr>
                      </thead>
                      <tbody id="dt-body">
                        <tr data-rowid="r1"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox dt-row-check"></td><td><a class="dt-link">MacBook-Pro-14</a></td><td>Laptop</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td><td>2 min ago</td><td>Aravinth M</td></tr>
                        <tr data-rowid="r2"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox dt-row-check"></td><td><a class="dt-link">iPhone-15-Pro</a></td><td>Mobile</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td><td>5 min ago</td><td>Priya R</td></tr>
                        <tr data-rowid="r3"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox dt-row-check"></td><td><a class="dt-link">Dell-XPS-Desk-01</a></td><td>Desktop</td><td><span class="dt-badge warning">Idle</span></td><td>1 hr ago</td><td>Kiran V</td></tr>
                        <tr data-rowid="r4"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox dt-row-check"></td><td><a class="dt-link">iPad-Air-5</a></td><td>Tablet</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td><td>12 min ago</td><td>Neha S</td></tr>
                        <tr data-rowid="r5"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox dt-row-check"></td><td><a class="dt-link">Pixel-8-Pro</a></td><td>Mobile</td><td><span class="dt-badge danger">Offline</span></td><td>3 days ago</td><td>Rahul K</td></tr>
                        <tr data-rowid="r6"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox dt-row-check"></td><td><a class="dt-link">Surface-Laptop-5</a></td><td>Laptop</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td><td>just now</td><td>Ananya P</td></tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                  </div>
                  <div class="dt-footer" id="dt-footer-row">
                    <div class="dt-footer-left">
                      <span>Rows per page</span>
                      <select class="dt-rows-select"><option>10</option><option selected>20</option><option>50</option><option>100</option></select>
                      <span style="margin-left:12px;">1&ndash;6 of 243</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dt-pagination">
                      <button class="dt-page-btn" disabled>&lsaquo; Previous</button>
                      <button class="dt-page-btn active">1</button>
                      <button class="dt-page-btn">2</button>
                      <button class="dt-page-btn">3</button>
                      <button class="dt-page-btn">Next &rsaquo;</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="dt-bulk-bar" id="dt-bulk-bar">
                    <div class="dt-bulk-left"><span id="dt-bulk-count">0 Selected</span></div>
                    <div class="dt-bulk-actions">
                      <button class="dt-bulk-btn"><svg width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg> Edit</button>
                      <button class="dt-bulk-btn"><svg width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/></svg> Export</button>
                      <button class="dt-bulk-btn danger"><svg width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="3 6 5 6 21 6"/><path d="M19 6l-2 14H7L5 6M10 11v6M14 11v6"/></svg> Delete</button>
                      <button class="dt-bulk-close" id="dt-bulk-close" title="Clear selection"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg></button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="content-guidelines" class="doc-h3">Content Guidelines<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);color:var(--prism-violet);">Recommended</span></h3>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li>Keep column headers short and noun-based ("Status", "Owner", "Due date").</li>
                <li>Put the primary link (the row's name / identifier) in the <strong>first</strong> data column.</li>
                <li>Align numeric columns to the end of the cell for scannability.</li>
                <li>Show <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">N Selected</code> and a clear-selection <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">&#10005;</code> in the bulk-action bar.</li>
                <li>Pair an empty state with a clear next action ("Add your first device").</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li>Write sentence-long headers &mdash; they break the column rhythm.</li>
                <li>Left-align numbers &mdash; they become hard to compare.</li>
                <li>Attach Delete to a per-row icon when the same action works in bulk.</li>
                <li>Cram every action into the main toolbar &mdash; it becomes noisy.</li>
                <li>Render a blank table with no guidance when empty.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== STYLE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-style" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="style-overview" class="doc-section-title">Style</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens, variant axes, and visual states that define the Data Table's appearance.</p>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="variants" class="doc-section-title">Variants</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Selection is the only variant axis. All other behaviour is controlled via component properties. The Figma set ships 2 variants.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Value</th><th>Description</th><th>Visual cue</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Default</code></td><td>No rows selected. Footer shows pagination controls only.</td><td>Normal row background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Selected</code></td><td>One or more rows checked. Selected rows have <code>BG-Selected</code> highlight; floating bulk-action bar overlays the footer center area.</td><td>Blue-tinted row background + dark floating pill</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="variant-matrix" class="doc-h3">Variant Matrix</h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:20px;">2 selection states &times; 2 toolbar toggles &times; 2 footer toggles &times; N rows &times; N columns = configurable at runtime.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Axis</th><th>Values</th><th>Note</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Selection</strong></td><td><code>Default</code>, <code>Selected</code></td><td>Only true variant axis in Figma (2 variants total).</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Toolbar</strong></td><td><code>true</code>, <code>false</code></td><td>Toggles top toolbar visibility.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Footer</strong></td><td><code>true</code>, <code>false</code></td><td>Toggles bottom footer visibility.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Column Count</strong></td><td><code>1&ndash;N</code></td><td>Driven by <code>columns</code> prop at runtime.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Row Count</strong></td><td><code>0&ndash;N</code></td><td>Driven by <code>rows</code> prop at runtime.</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="toolbar-variants" class="doc-h3">Toolbar Variants</h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Search + filter + overflow icon cluster on the right edge. The refresh icon appears before the search field when used.</p>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
              <div class="dt-wrapper" style="max-width:720px;">
                <div class="dt-toolbar">
                  <div class="dt-search" style="width:280px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg><input type="text" placeholder="Search..."></div>
                  <div style="flex:1;"></div>
                  <button class="dt-toolbar-btn with-label"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 4h18l-7 8v6l-4 2v-8z"/></svg> Filter</button>
                  <button class="dt-toolbar-btn"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1"/></svg></button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);">Default: search input + Filter dropdown + overflow (&#8942;).</div>
              <div class="dt-wrapper" style="max-width:720px;">
                <div class="dt-toolbar">
                  <button class="dt-toolbar-btn" title="Refresh"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h5M20 20v-5h-5M4 9a8 8 0 0114-4M20 15a8 8 0 01-14 4"/></svg></button>
                  <div class="dt-search" style="width:240px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg><input type="text" placeholder="Search..."></div>
                  <div style="flex:1;"></div>
                  <button class="dt-toolbar-btn with-label"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 4h18l-7 8v6l-4 2v-8z"/></svg> Filter</button>
                  <button class="dt-toolbar-btn"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/><circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1"/></svg></button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);">With refresh: refresh icon on the leading edge, then search + filter + overflow.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="column-header-states" class="doc-h3">Column Header States</h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Headers support sort affordances (asc / desc) and per-column filter icons.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:16px;">
              <div style="padding:20px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <table class="dt-table" style="border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;"><thead><tr><th style="padding:8px 12px;">Status</th></tr></thead></table>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-top:12px;">Default</div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:2px;">No sort / no filter</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <table class="dt-table" style="border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;"><thead><tr><th class="sortable sorted" style="padding:8px 12px;color:var(--prism-violet);">Status <svg class="sort-icon" width="10" height="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 15l-6-6-6 6"/></svg></th></tr></thead></table>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-top:12px;">Sorted Asc</div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:2px;">Up chevron, accent color</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <table class="dt-table" style="border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;"><thead><tr><th class="sortable sorted" style="padding:8px 12px;color:var(--prism-violet);">Status <svg class="sort-icon" width="10" height="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></th></tr></thead></table>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-top:12px;">Sorted Desc</div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:2px;">Down chevron, accent color</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:20px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <table class="dt-table" style="border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;"><thead><tr><th style="padding:8px 12px;">Status <svg width="10" height="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="vertical-align:middle;opacity:0.7;"><path d="M3 4h18l-7 8v6l-4 2v-8z"/></svg></th></tr></thead></table>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-top:12px;">With Filter</div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:2px;">Filter funnel adjacent</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="row-states" class="doc-h3">Row States</h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Rows render in four interactive states with subtle background changes.</p>
            <div class="dt-wrapper" style="max-width:720px;">
              <table class="dt-table">
                <thead><tr><th class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></th><th>Name</th><th>State</th></tr></thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>MacBook Pro</td><td><span style="color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-size:12px;">Default</span></td></tr>
                  <tr style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.04);"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>iPhone 15</td><td><span style="color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-size:12px;">Hover</span></td></tr>
                  <tr class="selected"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox" checked></td><td>Dell XPS 15</td><td><span style="color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-size:12px;">Selected</span></td></tr>
                  <tr class="disabled"><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox" disabled></td><td>iPad Air</td><td><span style="color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-size:12px;">Disabled</span></td></tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="color-tokens" class="doc-h3">Color Tokens<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);color:var(--prism-violet);">Tokens</span></h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Token</th><th>Role</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Primary-alt</code></td><td>Table body background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Secondary-alt</code></td><td>Header row background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Hover</code></td><td>Row hover background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Selected</code></td><td>Selected row background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Background/BG-Base-Dark</code></td><td>Floating bulk-action bar background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Border/Border-Secondary</code></td><td>Outer table border + horizontal row separators</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Border/Border-Tertiary</code></td><td>Vertical column separators (when enabled)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Primary</code></td><td>Cell text (default)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Tertiary</code></td><td>Header label, footer range, "Rows per page" label</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Link</code></td><td>Link-style cell text</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Inverse</code></td><td>Bulk-action bar text (on dark background)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Error</code></td><td>Destructive bulk action (Delete)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Text/Text-Success</code></td><td>Success badge in cells</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Shadow/Shadow-Medium</code></td><td>Floating bulk-action bar drop shadow</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="spacing-tokens" class="doc-h3">Spacing &amp; Radius Tokens</h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Token</th><th>Value</th><th>Usage</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>spacing/4</code></td><td>4 px</td><td>Badge internal spacing</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>spacing/8</code></td><td>8 px</td><td>Toolbar icon-to-input gap; footer inner gap</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>spacing/12</code></td><td>12 px</td><td>Cell horizontal padding</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>spacing/16</code></td><td>16 px</td><td>Toolbar / footer horizontal padding</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>border-radius/radius-8</code></td><td>8 px</td><td>Table outer frame</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>border-radius/radius-6</code></td><td>6 px</td><td>Bulk-action bar pill</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>border-radius/radius-4</code></td><td>4 px</td><td>Toolbar buttons, search input</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="typography" class="doc-h3">Typography</h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Element</th><th>Font</th><th>Size</th><th>Weight</th><th>Token</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Column header</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>13 px</td><td>Semibold (600)</td><td><code>body/Small/Medium</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Cell text</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>13 px</td><td>Regular (400)</td><td><code>body/Small/Default</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Cell link</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>13 px</td><td>Medium (500)</td><td><code>body/Small/Medium</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Badge text</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>12 px</td><td>Medium (500)</td><td><code>body/XSmall/Medium</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Toolbar placeholder</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>13 px</td><td>Regular (400)</td><td><code>body/Small/Default</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Footer "Rows per page"</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>12 px</td><td>Regular (400)</td><td><code>body/XSmall/Default</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Footer range / pagination</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>12 px</td><td>Regular (400)</td><td><code>body/XSmall/Default</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Bulk-action label</td><td>Zoho Puvi</td><td>13 px</td><td>Medium (500)</td><td><code>body/Small/Medium</code></td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="spacing-sizing" class="doc-h3">Spacing &amp; Sizing Reference</h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Row height &mdash; Compact</td><td>32 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Row height &mdash; Default</td><td><strong>40 px</strong></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Row height &mdash; Comfortable</td><td>48 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Header row height</td><td>40 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Toolbar height</td><td>48 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Footer height</td><td>48 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Bulk-action bar height</td><td>40 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Bulk-action bar corner radius</td><td>6 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Table outer radius</td><td>8 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Cell horizontal padding</td><td>12 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>First cell (checkbox column) width</td><td>40 px</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Row divider</td><td>1 px, <code>Border/Border-Secondary</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Header sticky offset</td><td>0 (sticks to scroll container top)</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Floating bar shadow</td><td><code>Shadow/Shadow-Medium</code></td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== USAGE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-usage" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="when-to-use" class="doc-section-title">When and Where to Use</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Data Table is designed for structured, record-based data that users need to scan, sort, select, and act on.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>When to use</h3>
                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">For <strong>structured, record-based data</strong> (tickets, devices, users, assets, incidents).</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When <strong>bulk actions</strong> (delete many, export many) are a core workflow.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When users compare rows on multiple attributes and <strong>column alignment is essential</strong>.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;">When per-row detail is deep enough that clicking a row should open a drawer or detail page.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#e42527" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>When NOT to use</h3>
                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Small static lists</strong> with 3&ndash;7 simple items &mdash; use a plain list.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Hierarchical / tree data</strong> &mdash; use a tree view or expandable rows.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;"><strong>Card-based content</strong> with rich imagery &mdash; use a card grid.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;"><strong>Dashboards of single values</strong> &mdash; use widgets / metric cards, not a table.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="density-guidance" class="doc-section-title">Density Guidance</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Choose row density based on data density, device, and user task.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Density</th><th>Row Height</th><th>Best for</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Compact</code></td><td>32 px</td><td>Power users scanning large tables; admin dashboards with high column count.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Default</code></td><td><strong>40 px</strong></td><td>Most product UIs. Balances scan speed with comfortable touch targets.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Comfortable</code></td><td>48 px</td><td>Mobile / tablet use; cells with multi-line content; first-time users.</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;">
                <div class="dt-wrapper"><table class="dt-table compact"><thead><tr><th class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></th><th>Name</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>MacBook</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr><tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>iPhone</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:8px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">Compact (32 px)</div>
              </div>
              <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;">
                <div class="dt-wrapper"><table class="dt-table"><thead><tr><th class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></th><th>Name</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>MacBook</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr><tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>iPhone</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:8px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">Default (40 px)</div>
              </div>
              <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;">
                <div class="dt-wrapper"><table class="dt-table comfortable"><thead><tr><th class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></th><th>Name</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>MacBook</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr><tr><td class="dt-check-cell"><input type="checkbox" class="dt-checkbox"></td><td>iPhone</td><td><span class="dt-badge success">Online</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
                <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:8px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">Comfortable (48 px)</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="detailed-guidelines" class="doc-section-title">Complete Do's and Don'ts</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for effective Data Table usage.</p>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li><strong>Short headers:</strong> Keep column headers short and noun-based ("Status", "Owner", "Due date").</li>
                <li><strong>Numeric alignment:</strong> Align numeric columns to the end of the cell.</li>
                <li><strong>Primary link first:</strong> Put the primary link (row's name / identifier) in the first data column.</li>
                <li><strong>Bulk destructive actions:</strong> Use the Selected variant's bulk-action bar for destructive actions (with confirmation).</li>
                <li><strong>Selection counter:</strong> Show 'N Selected' and a clear-selection &#10005; in the bulk-action bar.</li>
                <li><strong>Overflow menu:</strong> Use &#8942; for column chooser, density, export-all, and low-frequency actions.</li>
                <li><strong>Sticky header:</strong> Sticky the header row when the table scrolls.</li>
                <li><strong>Empty state CTA:</strong> Pair an empty state with a clear next action ("Add your first device").</li>
                <li><strong>Consistent height:</strong> Keep row height consistent within a single table.</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li><strong>Sentence headers:</strong> Write sentence-long headers.</li>
                <li><strong>Left-align numbers:</strong> Left-align numbers &mdash; they become hard to compare.</li>
                <li><strong>Buried primary link:</strong> Bury the primary link mid-row.</li>
                <li><strong>Per-row delete:</strong> Attach Delete to a per-row icon when the same action works in bulk.</li>
                <li><strong>Stale bulk bar:</strong> Leave the bulk bar visible when no rows are selected.</li>
                <li><strong>Crowded toolbar:</strong> Cram every action into the main toolbar &mdash; it becomes noisy.</li>
                <li><strong>Scrolling header:</strong> Let the header scroll away &mdash; users lose context.</li>
                <li><strong>Blank empty table:</strong> Render a blank table with no guidance when empty.</li>
                <li><strong>Mixed heights:</strong> Mix row heights based on content length.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

